    <h2 class="section-title">GE service across Greater Los Angeles.</h2>

    <p>GE Appliances has the most-installed base of any brand across our 5-county service area. Westside (Beverly Hills, Brentwood, Santa Monica, Pacific Palisades, Bel Air) leans heavily Profile and Café for renovation kitchens, with Monogram pro-ranges and built-in column refrigeration in the high-end homes; we've serviced Monogram column units in residences from Holmby Hills to Pacific Palisades to Bel Air. San Fernando Valley and Pasadena (Sherman Oaks, Studio City, Calabasas, Hidden Hills) sees a balanced mix, Profile and Café in mid-2010s and newer homes, base GE in older single-family. Inland Empire (Rancho Cucamonga, Fontana, Ontario, Temecula, Moreno Valley) is dominated by base-tier GE in production-builder homes from 2010-2020. Orange County (Newport Beach, Irvine, Costa Mesa, Anaheim, Laguna Beach) tracks similar Westside patterns with higher Monogram concentration in coastal luxury homes (Newport Coast, Laguna). Ventura County (Thousand Oaks, Camarillo, Simi Valley) sees strong Profile and base GE in the mid-2010s housing wave. The 8-branch dispatch grid in the hero CTA shows the closest dispatch territory for any address, Monogram-trained techs are dispatched specifically to luxury work; base GE and Profile route to the closest available branch with parts on the truck.</p>
